James Bush (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Bush_(actor) 0 James Bush (October 4, 1907 – April 9, 1987) was an American actor from the 1930s until the early 1950s. He appeared in over 100 television shows and films, over 80 of them being feature films. James_Bush ( October_4_,_1907 – April_9_,_1987 ) was an_American_actor from the_1930s until the_early_1950s .
